{"tid":400584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡若蓮長子潘匡仁　9月25日紅磡世界殯儀館設靈  翌日出殯","createTime":"2017-09-15T02:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T09:42:53.000Z","uid":79563,"like":112,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8939fdd1aff90e75a1f26be2260921692deabdda","tid":400584,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:15:06.000Z","msg":"上月出任教育局副局長的蔡若蓮，其患有抑鬱症的長子潘匡仁(25歲)早前墮樓身亡，據了解，潘匡仁將於9月25日(周一)在紅磡世界殯儀館世界堂設靈，翌日早上11時出殯，喪禮會以基督教儀式進行。據了解，蔡若蓮已於本周返回工作崗位。<br />\n<br />\n事發於上周四(9月7日)早上11時，洋名Peter的潘匡仁，在西九龍擎天半島41樓住所，攀出窗外曾被女傭發現奮力拉回，惟他掙脫並反鎖自己在房間內，未幾一躍而下倒臥屋苑平台，送院搶救後惜告不治。"},{"pid":"f1a4592172e1e84d16361b0128488d85de7d9187","tid":400584,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:18:08.000Z","msg":"r.i.p.囉"},{"pid":"bd7dc4692b67274ae3f6b02f3c4fff11c8d64c8f","tid":400584,"uid":42250,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:19:48.000Z","msg":"未過 probation 有冇扣人工？審計署睇緊 D 好喎"},{"pid":"be204b621375306474273e3fb17b0a4779fdbcb9","tid":400584,"uid":137604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:22:03.000Z","msg":"So9sad 囉"},{"pid":"f1f53202dc464bb22f3c27b9c49b25b9c802bd58","tid":400584,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0c5f2dcf80dbb08810013eb2ee26c49e4f5189","tid":400584,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>So9sad 囉</blockquote><br />\n90後唔捱得"},{"pid":"7049eec5a017a3766ab0777e53028f4a39a22a22","tid":400584,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未過 probation 有冇扣人工？審計署睇緊 D 好喎</blockquote><br />\n副局長邊會有probation<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/